{"id":168371,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011722/","date":"2011-07-24T05:00:22Z","modified":"2011-07-24T06:40:03Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/7/22_","content":"<p><p><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/23/business/global/china-mobile-executive-sentenced-to-death-over-bribes.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中移动高管因受贿被判死刑</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——北京在明年换届之前正掀起反腐败浪潮，其中有些案件带有打击政治对手的含义</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8654809/China-to-defy-Vatican-with-seven-new-bishops.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国不顾梵蒂冈反对，将再任命七名主教</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——不信神的共产党显然对管理神的事务很有兴趣</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8654765/China-disguises-motorway-as-vegetable-patch.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国把公路伪装成菜地</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——由于建路时没获批准，地方政府把它铺土撒种，糊弄检查人员</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8654710/Chinese-property-developers-scare-out-residents-with-scorpions.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国开发商用蝎子吓跑居民进行拆迁</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——深圳房地产开发商的创举令人心有余悸</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/8654045/Chinese-railways-corruption-probe-claims-another-scalp.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国铁路腐败案又揭出一人</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这是第三名被捕的中国铁道部高级官员</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">如是说博客：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.alsosprachanalyst.com/economy/chinas-high-speed-rail-story-going-bust.html?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+AlsoSprachAnalyst+%28Also+sprach+Analyst+%28Main%29%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的高铁泡沫即将破裂</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——开工之前的种种预测过于乐观，而现在铁道部面临着集资的困难，其债券不再畅销</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>Worldcrunch</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.worldcrunch.com/how-beijing-s-guardians-language-are-redefining-modern-china/3468\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京的“语言卫士”是如何重新定义现代中国的</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——最新版的《新华字典》收录了“农民工”，却没有收“防火墙”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东亚论坛：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eastasiaforum.org/2011/07/22/can-china-become-an-innovation-hub/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国有可能成为创新基地吗</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？——创新并不仅仅意味着研发投资，还意味着改变教学环境，鼓励创造力、独树一帜和批判性思考。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/forbes/2011/0808/opinions-lee-kuan-yew-current-events-challenge-in-pacific.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">太平洋地区的挑战：中国的崛起</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——李光耀在《福布斯》杂志上发表的社论，成中国如果能保持目前增长势头，必将与美国平起平坐</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/why-middle-class-matters-both-us-china-160928517.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么中产阶级对于中美都很重要</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国在设法扩大中产阶级人口，美国在设法阻止中产阶级消失</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国法律博客：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinalawblog.com/2011/07/noodle_blogs_your_absence_swells_my_eyes_with_tears_so_im_seeing_red_in_china.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">面条博客</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——介绍关于中国的一些英语博客。其中作者大力推荐的是“中国见红”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/spies-connected-to-china-said-to-have-carried-out-hacking-of-imf-computers.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">调查人员认为中国网络间谍窃取了国际货币基金组织的资料</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——黑客两次袭击，下载大量数据。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110722/bs_nm/us_britain_china_carriers\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">英国即将出售退役航母，中国买家伺机收购</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“很难猜测中国买主的动机，因为中国商人和共产党之间的关系颇为暧昧”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《连线》杂志：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/2011/07/chinese-e-bomb/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+WiredDangerRoom+(Blog+-+Danger+Room)\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">秘密文件揭示中国尚没有电磁炸弹</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——好消息是中国还没有微波炸弹，坏消息是中国对利用电磁辐射毁掉电脑很感兴趣</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《连线》杂志：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wired.com/wiredscience/2011/07/goodbye-space-shuttle/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">再见，航天飞机！现在可以开始太空竞赛了</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——航天飞机的终结并不意味着美国太空计划的终结，新的竞争刚刚开始</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2011/07/21/a_step_forward_then_a_step_back_in_south_china_sea_dispute\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">进一步又退一步的南海争端</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——有关各方刚刚达成了南海行为准则，但菲律宾议员随后就登上南沙群岛。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/asean-beat/2011/07/23/fishing-for-a-grey-zone/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">灰色渔区</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国在南海北部发布禁渔令，但越南是不会按令行事的</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">辛迪加项目：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.project-syndicate.org/commentary/karaganov16/English\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">俄罗斯，向东方看</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——按照目前趋势，乌拉尔山以东的俄国乃至整个国家，最终都会成为中国的附庸</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chovanec.wordpress.com/2011/07/22/wsj-chinese-banks-are-worse-off-than-you-think/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国银行的情况比你想象的要糟</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——较高的存贷比率掩藏了严重的坏债问题</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/07/22/changes-to-chinas-indigenous-innovation-policy-dont-get-too-excited/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国对“自主创新”政策的修改并不算大</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——外国公司想要借机挤入政府采购项目，仍需要与本地公司力拼</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-07-22/nokia-china-dominance-under-threat-as-sales-dive-on-android.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">诺基亚在中国的老大地位受到安卓威胁</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——诺基亚二季度在华销售额比上季度下降了一半，主要对手不仅仅是苹果</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/07/22/guest-post-falling-in-love-with-a-migrant-worker/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">爱上一名农民工</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——芬兰姑娘讲述自己在广州如何找到一位农民工当男朋友的故事</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>NPR</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.npr.org/2011/07/20/138536998/for-chinese-moms-birth-means-30-days-in-pajamas\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对于中国妈妈来说，生孩子就意味着要穿</span>30<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">天睡衣</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国传统的“坐月子”在美国人看来不可思议</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110722/ap_on_re_as/as_china_bus_fire\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国公共汽车失火，造成</span>41<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人死亡</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——河南新乡一辆双层客场起火，目前起火原因不明</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110722/ap_on_re_ca/cn_canada_chinese_fugitive\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">加拿大法官认定中国逃犯赖昌星不是难民</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——赖昌星即将被遣返。中国对此表示欢迎，并表示不会对赖施加酷刑或处以死刑。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《芝加哥论坛报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/chi-ap-il-fakeids-china,0,1782225.story\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">四十人因购买中国的假冒身份证明而被捕</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——芝加哥地区高中生和大学生通过互联网购买来自中国的假冒证件</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">福克斯新闻：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foxnews.com/health/2011/07/20/taste-test-swiss-chocolate-vs-made-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">瑞士巧克力与中国制造</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国一家研究机构对消费者心理做得一项有趣测试</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"><br /></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<div><i>友情提示：您可以到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>看到推友们对该篇译文的评论和转发；欢迎参与！如果您的电脑可以翻墙，请到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>的左栏参加我们的一个小调查</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-5357729857851897217?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":654,"categories":[1],"tags":[8840]}